<p>Dave&#39;s back from CES and he and John have all&nbsp;<em>that</em>&nbsp;to discuss as well as a full mailbag. Want to know about USB ports not being the same? Want to learn more about speeding up Safari? How about an automation tip for iOS that uses Hazel? The common theme? Sometimes your Mac lies to you (and your favorite geeks help you sort that out!).&nbsp;All this and more in today&#39;s episode, just for you!</p>
